T1  - Should Germany have built a new wall? Macroeconomic lessons from the 2015-18 refugee wave
AU  - Busch, Christopher
AU  - Krueger, Dirk
AU  - Ludwig, Alexander
AU  - Popova, Irina
AU  - Iftikhar, Zainab
JO  - Journal of Monetary Economics
VL  - 113
